17\/10\/25\/abu-darda-nifaq-khushu\/","url_meta":{"origin":37343,"position":0},"title":"Abu Darda on Nifaq: Beware of hypocrisy of reverence, humility","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Sa\u2019d reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cSeek refuge in Allah from the reverence of hypocrisy.\u201d It was said, \u201cWhat is the reverence of hypocrisy?\u201d Abu Darda said, \u201cIt is that you see the body in reverence, but the heart is not reverent.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22894,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/05\/09\/abu-darda-dua-akhlaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":37343,"position":1},"title":"Abu Darda on Akhlaq: Supplicating all night for good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Darda reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with them both, stood praying and weeping, saying, \u201cO Allah, you have made my form excellent, so make my character excellent.\u201d He continued until the morning and I said, \u201cO Abu Darda, you did not supplicate for anything but good character!\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21244,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/11\/20\/nifaq-lose-deen-one-trial\/","url_meta":{"origin":37343,"position":2},"title":"Abu Darda on Nifaq: Muslim might lose their religion after one trial","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 20, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Jubayr ibn Nufayr reported: I entered the residence of Abu Darda while he was standing and praying in his place of prayer. When he sat down, he began fervently to recite the testimony of faith and to seek refuge in Allah from hypocrisy. After he finished, I said, \u201cMay Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4206,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/05\/duties-allah-selves-family\/","url_meta":{"origin":37343,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Duties: Rights of Allah, your family, and yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, made a fellowship between Salman and Abu Darda. Salman visited Abu Darda and found his wife Umm Darda dressed in worn-out clothing. He asked her why she was like this. She said, \u201cYour brother Abu Darda is not interested\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25789,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/21\/abu-darda-on-marriage-husband-and-wife-should-try-to-please-each-other\/","url_meta":{"origin":37343,"position":4},"title":"Abu Darda on Marriage: Husband and wife should try to please each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim ibn Adham reported: Abu Darda said to his wife Umm Darda, may Allah be pleased with both of them, \u201cIf I become angry, then try to please me. If you become angry, then I will try to please you. Were we not to act this way, how quickly would\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23955,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/10\/31\/abu-darda-reconciliation\/","url_meta":{"origin":37343,"position":5},"title":"Abu Darda on Virtue: No deeds better than prayer, good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 31, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Idris reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cNo deeds of the children of Adam are better than walking to prayer, having exceptional character, and reconciling people.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd wal-Raqa\u0304\u2019iq 725 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0625\u0650\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0633\u064e \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u0628\u0648 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0631\u062f\u0627\u0621 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0622\u062f\u064e\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064c \u0639\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0644\u064b\u0627 \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064b\u0627 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dai